fashion
work
has
included
shooting
campaigns
and
catalogues
for
<ref target="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JW_Anderson">
JW
Anderson
</ref>
and
<ref target="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LOEWE_(fashion_brand)">
Loewe
</ref>
(
