in
collaboration
with
Jonathan
Anderson
)
,
<ref target="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Main_Page#cite_note-nytimes-wilkinson-7">
[
7
]
</ref>
<ref target="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Main_Page#cite_note-id-weinstock-8">
[
8
]
</ref>
and
editorials
for
<hi rend="italic">
<ref target="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vogue_(magazine)">
Vogue
</ref>
,
</hi>
<hi rend="italic">
<ref target="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fantastic_Man_(magazine)">
Fantastic
Man
</ref>
,
</hi>
and
<hi rend="italic">
<ref target="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/T:_The_New_York_Times_Style_Magazine">
T
:
